[MFC] CEdit cannot get mutil lines when input "\r\n"
[MFC] CEdit 输入"\r\n"无法回车显示

Question:
CEdit cannot get mutil lines when input "\r\n"
CEdit 输入"\r\n"无法回车显示

Reason:


Solution:
two ways:
1.when create Edit, adding "ES_MULTILINE" 
2. set "mutiline" true in the "dialog box"
两种方式：
1、在代码中通过create创建Edit控件必须加入ES_MULTILINE
2、对话框中添加的Edit控件需要将Multiline属性设置为true

2017-8-24
